'''Donnel Waynwood''' is a recurring character in the [[Season 4|fourth season]]. He is played by [[Alisdair Simpson]] and debuts in &quot;[[First of His Name]]&quot;. Ser Donnel Waynwood is a [[Knighthood|knight]] of [[House Waynwood]] and serves [[House Arryn]] as the [[Knight of the Gate]], commander of the [[Bloody Gate]].

